{"id":256392,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-重庆青年黄成城被劳教案，8次提起行政诉/","date":"2012-10-11T15:01:16Z","modified":"2012-10-11T15:01:16Z","title":"维权网 | 重庆青年黄成城被劳教案，8次提起行政诉讼法院不受理（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）重庆市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span><span>后青年黄成城，因于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，就网传的茉莉花集会事件，在网上发了请朋友喝“花茶”的相关帖子，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>被重庆市壁山县公安局抓捕，随后对黄成诚作出劳教两年的决定，黄成诚目前在重庆市北碚区的西山坪劳教所内关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黄成城对劳教决定不服，他姐姐帮助委托了重庆律师，但是当局不让律师介入。后来，他委托姐姐直接向重庆第一中级法院提起行政诉讼，共八次起诉未果。法院答复对这类敏感案件不予受理。他姐姐曾找市检察院、市人大常委会、市高级法院投诉，也没有任何作用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>，作为黄成城的委托代理人，浦志强律师向重庆第一中级法院提交了起诉材料，起诉重庆市劳教委。法院接受了材料，并开出了收据。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，浦志强律师赴重庆第一中级法院，替在劳教所内</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>服教</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的黄成城询问立案进展。陈劲松法官接待，表示能否立案已依法请示上级法院，他还无法答复。法院本应依法在接受起诉材料七日内决定是否立案，但一直没答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关详情请参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/08/blog-post_3540.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/08/blog-post_3540.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-q5t5A-Oc2Dc/UHaP7TaVYWI/AAAAAAAAQ9M/GiiNOZVnziU/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-q5t5A-Oc2Dc/UHaP7TaVYWI/AAAAAAAAQ9M/GiiNOZVnziU/s320/5.jpg\" width=\"252\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8045291269217397675?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}